value function abs.)

EOT

ANS(fun_cmp("2+abs(x-1)", vars=>["x"]));

TEXT(EV3(<<'EOT'));
$BR Hint: 
Ask what happens to the vertex of the graph.
EOT

SOLUTION(EV3(<<'EOT'));
$BR $BBOLD Solution:$EBOLD
The vertex of the modified function is at \((1,2)\).
To move it there we replace \(f(x) = |x|\) with
\(g(x) = |x-1| + 2.\)
